adidas Campus 80s South Park Towelie
results.story: The South Park x adidas Campus 80 ‘Towelie’ showcases a unique build inspired by the animated series’ talking towel character. The low-top makes use of a lavender terry-cloth upper with contrasting white leather on the Trefoil-branded heel tab and signature three-stripes. Each tongue is decorated with Towelie’s cartoon eyes, which become pink and bloodshot when exposed to UV light. The interior tongue is equipped with a stash pocket and inscribed with a pair of mismatched quotes: ‘Don’t Forget to Bring a Towel’ on the left shoe and ‘I Have No Idea What’s Going On’ on the right.

adidas D Rose 11 Boardwalk
results.story: The adidas D Rose 11 ‘Boardwalk’ revisits a familiar color scheme previously showcased on the D Rose 4 and D Rose 10. This pair makes use of an Adizero textile upper in a vibrant Prism Mint finish. Contrasting pops of Red Zest make their way to the breathable mesh tongue, textile collar lining and featherweight Lightstrike midsole, reinforced with a lateral TPU support that extends up and around the heel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a traction pattern borrowed from the D Rose 7.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 2021 Crystal White Hazy Green
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Crystal White Hazy Green’ spotlights the running shoe’s full-length Boost midsole with a metallic iridescent finish. The responsive cushioning technology is reinforced underfoot by adidas’ Linear Energy Push torsion system and a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole. Up top, breathable Primeknit construction in Crystal White features recycled Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester. A molded heel counter in Hazy Green offers rearfoot stability.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA DFB
results.story: The DFB x adidas UltraBoost DNA ‘Triple Black’ celebrates the Germany national football team with a stealthy one-note finish. The sneaker’s all-black Primeknit upper incorporates recycled Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester. Four tonal stars are stamped on a webbing pull tab at the heel, while the tongue is adorned with a translucent national team crest. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length Boost midsole, painted black and supported by a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas D Rose 11 White Black Speckled
results.story: The adidas D Rose 11 ‘White Black Speckled’ delivers a clean colorway of Derrick Rose’s eleventh signature shoe, highlighted by a pristine white Adizero textile upper. A subtle off-white finish distinguishes the molded tongue and padded collar, featuring adidas and Rose branding, respectively. Light speckling is applied to a Lightstrike midsole with a reinforced TPU support on the lateral sidewall. An icy translucent rubber outsole offers grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: adidas Dame 7 Jam Fest
results.colorway: Signal Cyan/Team Shock Pink/Team Solar Green
results.story: Inspired by the retro basketball video game, the adidas Dame 7 ‘Jam Fest’ floods Damian Lillard’s signature shoe with an eye-catching turquoise hue. An engineered lacing system extends from the midfoot to the heel, securing a breathable mesh upper fortified with a series of tonal synthetic overlays that provide lightweight support. A matching turquoise finish is applied to the Lighstrike foam midsole, reinforced by a grippy rubber outsole that enables quick movements on the hardwood.

results.name: Undefeated x Neighborhood x ZX 8000 'White Gum'
results.story: Releasing as part of a capsule collection that reunites the LA retailer and Tokyo streetwear brand, the Undefeated x Neighborhood x adidas ZX 8000 ‘White Gum’ delivers a pristine colorway of the retro runner. The upper is constructed from white technical mesh with tonal leather overlays and silver reflective accents at the toe and heel. Mismatched Undefeated and Neighborhood branding appears on the sneaker’s left and right tongues, both of which are equipped with a zippered stash pocket. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a textured EVA midsole, reinforced underfoot by a gum rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas ZX 8000 Sean Wotherspoon Superearth
results.story: Launching as part of the brand’s sprawling 26-part A-ZX series, the Sean Wotherspoon x adidas ZX 8000 ‘Super Earth’ delivers the Round Two founder’s eye-catching interpretation of the classic running shoe. A patchwork-like mix of different textiles makes up the composition of the upper, ranging from pastel plaid to rustic canvas. The sneaker’s medial side is sprinkled with multicolor embroidered Trefoils, while the opposite side features embroidered florals with cascading runoff threads. Super Earth branding adorns the tongue and heel, the latter reinforced with a transparent heel counter.

results.name: Undefeated x Neighborhood x ZX 8000 'Black Gum'
results.story: The Undefeated x Neighborhood x adidas ZX 8000 ‘Black Gum’ is taken from a larger collaboration between the LA retailer and Japanese streetwear brand. The vintage runner carries a black technical mesh upper with tonal nubuck overlays and 3M reflective detailing. Mismatched Neighborhood and Undefeated branding is applied to the right and left tongue, both of which are equipped with a zippered stash pocket. Additional branding hits land on the eyestay and heel tab. The sneaker rides on a matching black EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a gum rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Superstar Primeblue Chalk White
results.story: The adidas Superstar Primeblue ‘White Black’ updates the iconic silhouette with refreshed detailing and a sustainable build. Primeblue branding is displayed on the lateral side, indicating that the white textile upper incorporates upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic, highlighted by a black netting-like overlay that wraps around the heel. Semi-translucent rubber is utilized on the sneaker’s shell toe and durable cupsole, the latter featuring a traditional herringbone tread underfoot.

Parley x Terrex Free Hiker 'Aluminium Sesame'
results.story: The Parley x adidas Terrex Free Hiker ‘Aluminium Sesame’ applies a neutral monochromatic finish to an outdoor silhouette build in part with upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic, recovered from beaches and coastal communities before it floats out into the ocean. The sock-like upper is constructed from coated Primeknit textile with tonal no-sew overlays and a molded TPU heel counter. A stacked full-length Boost midsole is supported by an EVA stabilization frame and reinforced underfoot by a lugged Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: Marvel x Predator Freak.3 FG J 'Cyclops'
Marvel x X Ghosted+ Laceless FG J 'Cyclops'
Parley x Terrex Free Hiker 'Earth Trace Cargo'
results.story: The Parley x adidas Terrex Free Hiker ‘Earth Trace Cargo’ showcases a military-inspired palette on a rugged outdoor silhouette constructed with sustainability in mind. Upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic is incorporated into the charcoal-colored Primeknit upper, equipped with an elastic cuff and fortified with synthetic no-sew overlays. Responsive cushioning is provided by a khaki-hued Boost midsole, reinforced with an EVA stabilization frame for lateral support. Underfoot, a lugged Continental rubber outsole provides enhanced traction.

results.name: Parley x Terrex Free Hiker 'Black'
results.story: The Parley x adidas Terrex Free Hiker ‘Black’ delivers a stealthy edition of a lightweight trail shoe stripped of all color. Made in part with upcycled Parley Ocean Plastic, the sneaker-boot hybrid carries a breathable Primeknit upper equipped with an elastic cuff and a webbing pull loop at the heel. The mid-top is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole in a matching black finish. Underfoot, the Adaptive Traxion outsole features Continental rubber for grippy traction on uneven terrain.

results.name: Wmns Terrex Swift R3 GTX 'Hazy Emerald'
adidas Yeezy 500 High Frosted Blue
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 500 High ‘Frosted Blue’ showcases a contrasting two-tone color palette on a retro-inspired lifestyle sneaker that traces a lineage to the adidas KB8 III. The upper is composed of stretchy elastane in a vibrant blue finish, fortified with suede overlays in a lighter blue shade. They’re joined by tan suede on the sneaker’s segmented eyestay and reinforced toe wrap. Additional details include toggle lacing and a padded, high-cut collar. Cushioning arrives via a podular adiPRENE midsole that gives the nod to adidas’ Feet You Wear technology.

results.name: Pharrell x Superstar Primeknit 'White'
results.story: The Pharrell x Superstar Primeknit ‘White’ offers the creative’s pristine take on the vintage sneaker. White Primeknit is utilized on the upper, featuring woven construction that mimics the iconic shell toe. A small Trefoil tag in Vivid Green is added to the medial collar, matching an inverted adidas wordmark on the tongue and ‘Humanrace’ embroidered on the heel tab. Pharrell’s signature reflexology graphic adorns the sockliner. The low-top is mounted on a standard Superstar cupsole, complete with a herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Five Ten Impact Pro Mid 'Black Red'
results.story: The adidas Five Ten Impact Pro Mid ‘Black Red’ delivers a mountain biking shoe that can withstand wet and muddy conditions. Built with a mid-cut collar for added support and protection, the quick-drying synthetic upper is rendered in a sleek black finish with crimson Five Ten branding on the lateral quarter panel. A matching black finish is applied to a compression-molded polyurethane midsole, reinforced with a Stealth S1 Dotty tread outsole that ensures feet stay on the pedals.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'White Ivory Blue'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘White Ivory Blue’ pairs classic tennis style with a modern, sustainable build. The white synthetic leather upper is made with 50% recycled content and features familiar perforated three-stripe branding on the side panels. An adidas Trefoil is stamped on the pale blue heel tab, while a contrasting beige tongue is marked with the iconic Stam Smith logo. The low-top rides on a durable rubber cupsole that’s unchanged from the original.

results.name: Pharrell x Superstar Primeknit 'Black'
results.story: The Pharrell x adidas Superstar Primeknit ‘Black’ delivers the visionary creative’s interpretation of the classic silhouette. Traditional leather construction is replaced by flexible Primeknit, complete with woven detailing that replicates the look of the iconic shell toe. The all-black finish is disrupted by Vivid Green branding hits, including ‘Humanrace’ embroidered on the heel tab and an inverted adidas wordmark on the tongue. The lightweight build is mounted on a matching black rubber cupsole.

results.name: Wmns SL Andridge 'Glow Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s SL Andridge ‘Glow Pink’ delivers a subtle colorway of a lifestyle silhouette that borrows liberally from ‘70s running shoes. Ghillie-style lacing secures an upper crafted from beige textile with tonal leather overlays at the toe and heel. Matching leather three-stripes are enlivened with exposed zigzag stitching. The sneaker rides on an exaggerated midsole in a blend of EVA and TPU, supported underfoot by a pink-hued rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'Halo Ivory'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘Halo Ivory’ updates the iconic silhouette with a tan synthetic leather upper made with 50% recycled content. The sustainable build comes replete with signature Stan Smith details, including tonal stitching, perforated three-stripes and a Trefoil logo stamped on the heel tab. adidas’ Primegreen branding adorns the sockliner, indicating that the shoe contains zero virgin plastic. A standard white rubber cupsole anchors the low-top.

results.name: Five Ten Kestrel Pro Boa 'Black Red'
results.story: The adidas Five Ten Kestrel Pro Boa ‘Black Red’ treats the mountain biking shoe to stealthy finish and a sustainable build. Recycled materials make up part of the composition of the weather-resistant synthetic upper, secured with a Boa lacing system and adjustable forefoot strap. The sneaker is mounted on a matching black EVA midsole that’s reinforced with a carbon-infused nylon shank. Underfoot, a Stealth C4 rubber outsole delivers optimal grip.

results.name: adidas City Series Wien Blue Tint
results.story: The adidas Wien SPZL ‘City Series’ brings back an archival silhouette that pays homage to Vienna, Austria. A rich royal blue finish is applied to the soft suede upper, reinforced with a toe overlay and marked with gold-foil ‘Wien’ branding. Contrasting orange accents make their way to the heel tab, serrated three-stripes and leather collar lining, the latter engraved with ‘City Series MMXXI.’ The low-profile lace-up is mounted on a semi-translucent gum rubber cupsole.

results.name: D.O.N. Issue #2 'Championship'
results.story: The adidas D.O.N. Issue #2 ‘Championship’ updates Donovan Mitchell’s second signature shoe with a tonal black finish and metallic gold detailing throughout. On the black mesh upper, gold streaks are complemented by a medial-side gold overlay stamped with ‘Championship’ in contrasting black lettering. Additional gilded accents land on branding hits at the tongue and molded heel. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a black Bounce midsole covered in gold speckling.

results.name: adidas ZX 8000 Out There
results.story: The adidas ZX 8000 ‘Out There’ delivers a rugged interpretation of the vintage runner. Breathable black canvas is utilized on the upper, accented with tiger camo detailing and interchangeable hook-and-loop straps that display various city names, years and zip codes. A removable snap-button pocket features the same tiger camo print and a convenient transparent window. The sneaker rides on a lightly speckled EVA midsole, reinforced underfoot by a decoupled gum rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA Lego
results.story: The LEGO x adidas UltraBoost DNA features transparent three-stripes that holds multicolored LEGO plates for a custom mix-and-match aesthetic. The rest of the upper is constructed from white Primeknit that incorporates recycled Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester. A metallic silver finish shines on the heel counter and forefoot overlay, while the toe box features a distinctive texture that replicates the look of LEGO bricks. Dual adidas and LEGO branding adorns the tongue and custom sockliner.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA 1.0 ZX 6000
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 1.0 DNA ‘ZX 6000’ combines a retro running aesthetic with a contemporary performance build. While the Primeknit upper features woven construction modeled after the original UltraBoost from 2015, the familiar color scheme recalls the OG ZX 6000 that debuted in 1989 alongside adidas’ iconic Torsion system. Adding to the sneaker’s vintage look are a suede forefoot overlay and an off-white finish on the Boost midsole. Underfoot, the Stretchweb outsole uses Continental rubber for grippy traction.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA 1.0 Aqua ZX 8000
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 1.0 DNA ‘ZX 8000’ replicates the look of the iconic running shoe from 1988, highlighted by an OG-inspired color scheme that blends a light teal base with contrasting yellow and violet accents. The breathable Primeknit upper is modeled after the original UltrBoost from 2015 and fortified with a suede forefoot overlay that nods to the ZX 8000. Responsive cushioning comes courtesy of an aqua-colored Boost midsole, supported by adidas’ Torsion bar and a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA 1.0 ZX 9000
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 1.0 DNA ‘ZX 9000’ features a familiar design steeped in the brand’s running heritage. In addition to a Primeknit upper that uses the same woven construction as the original UltraBoost from 2015, the vibrant palette gives the nod to the OG ZX 9000. Bright aqua coloring up top is countered by a full-length Boost midsole, rendered in an off-white finish for a vintage aesthetic. Underfoot, a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole delivers grippy traction.

results.name: Y-3 Forum Hi OG 'Triple Black'
results.story: The adidas Y-3 Forum Hi OG ‘Triple Black’ delivers Yohji Yamamoto’s fashion-forward take on the retro hoops shoe. A stealthy monochromatic finish is executed on the all-leather upper, secured with an updated ankle strap and zippered detailing that wraps around the heel and extends down the lateral midfoot. The high-top is mounted on a matching black rubber cupsole modeled after the original Forum, complete with a medial-side EVA wedge covered in Dillinger webbing.

results.name: Y-3 Runner 4D IOW 'Black'
results.story: The adidas Y-3 Runner 4D IOW ‘Black’ showcases a sleek finish on a versatile runner that comes with detachable details. Wearers can opt for a Primeknit sock or a more conventional sockliner and removable tongue. A black mesh overlay envelops the upper and extends to the groundbreaking 3D-printed midsole, crafted from a blend of light, oxygen and liquid resin. Lattice-like sidewalls are exposed through cutaway detailing around the forefoot.

results.name: Wmns UltraBoost 4.0 DNA 'White Cream'
results.story: The adidas women’s UltraBoost 4.0 DNA ‘White Cream’ utilizes a Primeknit upper in a subtle blend of tan and cream fibers. The breathable knit build, made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic and lined in comfortable textile, rests on a full-length Boost midsole in a pristine white finish. Branding hits include a discreet adidas tongue tag and ‘UltraBoost’ embossed on the molded heel counter. Underfoot, a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole delivers optimal grip.

results.name: UltraBoost DNA CC_1 'Cloud White Gradient'
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost DNA CC_1 ‘Cloud White Gradient’ takes inspiration from the cult-favorite ClimaCool 1, highlighted by a textured Primeknit upper that incorporates Parley Ocean Plastic. Further nods to the retro silhouette include a two-tone ClimaCool tongue tag and a layered RPU cage with ventilated air channels. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length Boost midsole, rendered in a gradient blue finish and supported by a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: UltraBoost 4.0 DNA 'Grey'
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 4.0 DNA ‘Grey’ dresses the lightweight running shoe in a charcoal Primeknit upper made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic. The sneaker’s lacing system is integrated into the midfoot cage for a lockdown fit, while a molded heel counter cradles the back of the foot for enhanced support and stability. Energy return is generated by a full-length Boost midsole, which is supported underfoot by a flexible Stretchweb outsole built with grippy Continental rubber.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 5.0 DNA Scarlet Black Gradient
adidas Forum Low Bad Bunny Pink Easter Egg
results.story: The Bad Bunny x adidas Forum Buckle Low ‘Easter Egg’ represents the pastel-colored follow-up to the duo’s inaugural ‘First Cafe’ collaboration, which preceded this holiday-themed release by less than a month. adidas’ retro hoops shoe is updated with a leather and suede build, rendered in subtle pink and coral hues and revamped with modern details. They include an adjustable ankle strap and doubled-up tongues, both featuring Bad Bunny’s third-eye logo. A durable rubber cupsole with semi-translucent sidewalls anchors the low-top.

results.name: adidas Dame 7 Fine China
results.story: The adidas Dame 7 ‘Fine China’ replicates the look of porcelain tableware with red and blue prints depicting dragons, leaves and clouds. The ornate designs are applied to the tongue, heel, Lightstrike midsole and translucent rubber outsole, while the majority of the sneaker’s textile upper is rendered in a clean white finish. Additional embellishments include Damian Lillard’s personal logo embroidered on the tongue and ‘Gift to the World’ inscribed on contrasting red insoles.

results.name: adidas Dame 7 Fire Of Greatness
results.story: The adidas Dame 7 ‘Fire Inside’ treats Damian Lillard’s signature shoe to a bold monochromatic finish inspired by Chinese lanterns. An integrated lacing system secures the breathable textile upper, lined with internal cushioning pods and reinforced with tonal synthetic leather at the toe and heel. ‘Fire of Greatness’ is inscribed on the lace keeper stitched atop the tongue, while the sockliner is marked with text that reads ‘Gift to the World.’ A full-length Lightstrike midsole in a matching Solar Red hue provides a combination of stability and energy return.

results.name: adidas DON Issue 2 Dragons and Clouds
results.story: The adidas D.O.N. Issue #2 ‘Kumu Clouds & Dragon’ enlivens Donovan Mitchell’s second signature shoe with a Japanese-inspired print throughout the textile upper. An engineered cord lacing system provides a feeling of lockdown, while a molded heel counter hugs the back of the foot for enhanced rearfoot stability. The low-top is mounted on a responsive Bounce midsole, supported by a translucent rubber outsole that wraps up the medial toe for added durability and traction.
